WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.786 --> 00:00:07.443
EliA

2
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:15.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

3
00:03:56.833 --> 00:03:59.416
Cheers!

4
00:04:07.958 --> 00:04:09.333
Excellent.

5
00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:12.500
Let's drink until we drop.

6
00:04:12.541 --> 00:04:14.375
Save something for your wife.

7
00:04:14.625 --> 00:04:17.458
Are you kidding?

8
00:04:17.916 --> 00:04:20.041
Alcohol revives me.

9
00:04:20.458 --> 00:04:23.083
The later it gets. the hornier I get.

10
00:04:24.958 --> 00:04:27.375
Another glass. A little sip.

11
00:04:30.541 --> 00:04:32.500
Tell me. Jane...

12
00:04:32.916 --> 00:04:34.125
What year are you in?

13
00:04:34.833 --> 00:04:35.708
4th year.

14
00:04:35.958 --> 00:04:37.875
A senior should know better.

15
00:04:38.333 --> 00:04:41.041
What are you doing with Tun?

16
00:04:41.375 --> 00:04:42.750
He's a hunk.

17
00:04:43.458 --> 00:04:45.416
You keep saying that.

18
00:04:45.916 --> 00:04:48.583
Making Jim ask for girl's numbers.

19
00:04:48.625 --> 00:04:49.750
Then breaking their hearts.

20
00:04:49.791 --> 00:04:52.416
Speaking of broken hearts...

21
00:04:53.041 --> 00:04:54.916
Remember the time...

22
00:04:54.958 --> 00:04:57.666
that girl left him a drunken mess.

23
00:04:58.750 --> 00:05:00.833
Her name was Kay.

24
00:05:01.083 --> 00:05:03.041
Ignore them.

25
00:05:03.958 --> 00:05:05.833
Wait. I have a question.

26
00:05:06.208 --> 00:05:08.083
How can a guy like you get married?

27
00:05:08.125 --> 00:05:09.833
What's wrong with me?

28
00:05:10.541 --> 00:05:13.250
After a long tiring day...

29
00:05:13.583 --> 00:05:15.416
I want to head home...

30
00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:18.166
to a wife's embrace or a pet's face.

31
00:05:18.208 --> 00:05:20.208
Not waste my life...

32
00:05:20.250 --> 00:05:23.333
partying with you losers.

33
00:05:23.375 --> 00:05:24.750
Not with me.

34
00:05:25.333 --> 00:05:26.750
A good man...

35
00:05:26.791 --> 00:05:29.833
who went whoring with me last night.

36
00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:32.791
Fooling around so soon?

37
00:05:34.166 --> 00:05:35.708
Here she comes.

38
00:05:38.083 --> 00:05:39.208
Quiet.

39
00:05:39.250 --> 00:05:40.875
What's so funny?

40
00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.041
Nothing.

41
00:05:43.625 --> 00:05:45.916
One last thing...

42
00:05:46.541 --> 00:05:48.291
One more glass!

43
00:06:08.291 --> 00:06:10.333
What are we listening to?

44
00:06:11.916 --> 00:06:13.833
Don't turn it off.

45
00:06:13.875 --> 00:06:15.250
It's beautiful.

46
00:06:17.750 --> 00:06:19.500
You guys seem tight.

47
00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:21.958
Do you meet often?

48
00:06:25.375 --> 00:06:26.916
What are you looking at?

49
00:06:27.458 --> 00:06:28.875
Beautiful you.

50
00:06:31.333 --> 00:06:33.375
What a sap.

51
00:07:16.458 --> 00:07:17.500
Are you hurt?

52
00:07:19.750 --> 00:07:20.750
Tun...

53
00:07:21.958 --> 00:07:22.875
Is she dead?

54
00:07:32.416 --> 00:07:33.333
Wait!

55
00:07:43.583 --> 00:07:44.666
Drive away.

56
00:07:45.875 --> 00:07:47.166
I said drive away!

57
00:07:48.583 --> 00:07:50.333
Drive away!

58
00:08:00.875 --> 00:08:02.666
Get closer. please.

59
00:08:03.041 --> 00:08:04.291
Okay.

60
00:08:05.208 --> 00:08:06.791
Big smile. Nuch.

61
00:08:07.333 --> 00:08:09.166
Or you won't look pretty.

62
00:08:17.458 --> 00:08:19.458
All Science Majors...

63
00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:21.666
gather for a class photo.

64
00:08:22.458 --> 00:08:23.750
They're calling you.

65
00:08:24.250 --> 00:08:25.791
Where's Jane?

66
00:08:27.291 --> 00:08:29.958
Taking photos with her friends.

67
00:08:30.791 --> 00:08:33.833
I thought maybe you broke up.

68
00:08:34.250 --> 00:08:36.583
Come! Let's go.

69
00:09:33.291 --> 00:09:35.583
I phoned but you didn't pick up.

70
00:09:35.958 --> 00:09:37.375
Was it on silent?

71
00:09:46.416 --> 00:09:48.666
Nuch asked about you today.

72
00:09:51.666 --> 00:09:53.958
When will you be free?

73
00:09:54.250 --> 00:09:55.958
She wants to...

74
00:10:18.083 --> 00:10:19.041
Jane.

75
00:10:21.166 --> 00:10:23.750
How can you act like this?

76
00:10:26.791 --> 00:10:29.291
Pretending nothing happened.

77
00:10:31.041 --> 00:10:32.416
Since that night...

78
00:10:32.458 --> 00:10:34.166
I haven't slept soundly.

79
00:10:38.458 --> 00:10:40.583
I'm upset as well.

80
00:10:42.458 --> 00:10:45.166
At least we should have checked.

81
00:10:46.875 --> 00:10:48.916
It was an accident.

82
00:10:50.291 --> 00:10:51.958
That's easy for you to say.

83
00:10:53.666 --> 00:10:56.041
You weren't behind the wheel...

84
00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.583
Hi. Ti. / Hey.

85
00:11:10.166 --> 00:11:11.958
How's business?

86
00:11:12.375 --> 00:11:14.416
With you here this early...

87
00:11:14.750 --> 00:11:16.833
business should be bad.

88
00:11:18.625 --> 00:11:20.458
Are my prints ready?

89
00:11:21.500 --> 00:11:23.416
Yeah. Just a sec.

90
00:11:28.291 --> 00:11:29.083
Here.

91
00:11:53.750 --> 00:11:55.291
Is your processor broken?

92
00:11:56.583 --> 00:11:57.833
Let's see.

93
00:12:02.958 --> 00:12:04.125
The nerve.

94
00:12:04.416 --> 00:12:06.166
Nice prints and you're great.

95
00:12:06.458 --> 00:12:08.666
If they suck it's my fault.

96
00:12:08.958 --> 00:12:11.041
Let's check the negative.

97
00:12:11.375 --> 00:12:12.583
No way.

98
00:12:12.958 --> 00:12:14.416
I took them. I should know.

99
00:12:14.666 --> 00:12:15.666
We'll see.

100
00:12:18.125 --> 00:12:19.125
See.

101
00:12:20.500 --> 00:12:22.833
Your negatives are bad.

102
00:12:46.458 --> 00:12:47.458
Tun.

103
00:12:58.333 --> 00:12:59.166
Tun.

104
00:13:17.333 --> 00:13:18.333
Tun.

105
00:13:20.666 --> 00:13:22.291
Can you hear me?

106
00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:32.000
Help!

107
00:15:33.666 --> 00:15:34.875
Help!

108
00:16:09.083 --> 00:16:11.833
Don't be scared. I'm here now.

109
00:16:32.458 --> 00:16:34.583
What's wrong with your camera?

110
00:16:35.083 --> 00:16:36.541
I don't know.

111
00:16:36.583 --> 00:16:38.791
The whole roll is ruined.

112
00:16:40.583 --> 00:16:42.375
That many?

113
00:16:48.375 --> 00:16:50.250
What are these shadows?

114
00:16:51.041 --> 00:16:52.833
My camera must be broken.

115
00:16:54.833 --> 00:16:57.125
How should I tell Nuch?

116
00:17:00.875 --> 00:17:01.750
Tun...

117
00:17:03.666 --> 00:17:05.291
Look at this picture.

118
00:17:16.708 --> 00:17:17.958
That woman...

119
00:17:19.208 --> 00:17:20.750
Do you think she's dead?

120
00:17:21.458 --> 00:17:22.791
That's enough.

121
00:17:28.958 --> 00:17:31.083
I'll have my camera fixed tomorrow.

122
00:18:35.375 --> 00:18:36.166
Tun...

123
00:18:36.416 --> 00:18:38.041
Look at this picture.

124
00:19:02.875 --> 00:19:04.666
Are you sure it was here?

125
00:19:12.041 --> 00:19:13.125
Excuse me.

126
00:19:13.166 --> 00:19:14.416
What happened?

127
00:19:15.958 --> 00:19:18.541
A few days ago a car hit the billboard.

128
00:19:18.583 --> 00:19:20.166
Must have been drunk.

129
00:19:21.958 --> 00:19:24.041
Was anyone hurt?

130
00:19:25.125 --> 00:19:26.125
No.

131
00:19:26.916 --> 00:19:28.208
Just the broken sign.

132
00:19:28.250 --> 00:19:29.416
Are you sure?

133
00:19:30.041 --> 00:19:31.083
What?

134
00:19:32.875 --> 00:19:34.291
Nothing.

135
00:19:35.500 --> 00:19:36.750
Thank you.

136
00:19:38.625 --> 00:19:39.916
What?

137
00:19:42.125 --> 00:19:44.833
You sure you checked everywhere?

138
00:19:48.166 --> 00:19:49.166
Nothing.

139
00:19:50.041 --> 00:19:51.666
Thanks anyways.

140
00:19:56.375 --> 00:19:59.458
He called every precinct and hospital.

141
00:20:00.541 --> 00:20:04.083
No accidents were reported that night.

142
00:20:04.583 --> 00:20:06.166
That's not possible.

143
00:20:07.250 --> 00:20:09.250
What about the girl we hit?

144
00:20:10.750 --> 00:20:13.291
You sure he called every one?

145
00:20:13.750 --> 00:20:15.708
Maybe someone helped her.

146
00:20:16.208 --> 00:20:18.166
Maybe she's fine.

147
00:20:18.208 --> 00:20:19.833
How could she be fine?

148
00:20:19.875 --> 00:20:21.875
We ploughed her down.

149
00:20:24.500 --> 00:20:26.875
And even if she's fine...

150
00:20:28.125 --> 00:20:30.041
Something is in those pictures.

151
00:20:30.458 --> 00:20:33.250
I told you they're not related to her.

152
00:20:33.541 --> 00:20:35.041
They're just bad exposures.

153
00:20:35.083 --> 00:20:36.125
Get it?

154
00:21:40.333 --> 00:21:41.333
Tun...

155
00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:44.250
You need to make some merit.

156
00:21:45.208 --> 00:21:46.333
These pictures...

157
00:21:46.958 --> 00:21:49.666
show that a spirit is haunting you.

158
00:21:55.750 --> 00:21:58.500
How long have you been a photographer?

159
00:21:58.541 --> 00:22:00.250
Why are you showing me these?

160
00:22:00.500 --> 00:22:01.666
I know...

161
00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:04.875
But don't you find these shadows strange?

162
00:22:06.916 --> 00:22:08.625
You want to see spirits?

163
00:22:09.166 --> 00:22:10.666
I'll show you some.

164
00:22:18.791 --> 00:22:19.750
Here.

165
00:22:20.333 --> 00:22:21.666
Auntie Cham's spirit.

166
00:22:22.625 --> 00:22:24.166
You know where she is now?

167
00:22:26.958 --> 00:22:30.166
She's selling grilled bananas next door.

168
00:22:31.708 --> 00:22:33.375
Here's Auntie Cham. And here.

169
00:22:33.875 --> 00:22:35.416
All Auntie Cham.

170
00:22:35.458 --> 00:22:36.875
Taken on the same day.

171
00:22:37.208 --> 00:22:38.708
They're just double exposures...

172
00:22:39.041 --> 00:22:40.333
and out of focus.

173
00:22:41.333 --> 00:22:44.333
Come on. I know that.

174
00:22:52.666 --> 00:22:55.333
Everyone is familiar with this place.

175
00:22:56.416 --> 00:22:59.291
Just an ordinary location...

176
00:23:00.333 --> 00:23:01.750
that we pass...

177
00:23:02.458 --> 00:23:04.583
and see everyday.

178
00:23:09.875 --> 00:23:12.000
Now look at these pictures...

179
00:23:15.916 --> 00:23:19.250
taken of the same place.

180
00:23:19.625 --> 00:23:20.833
In these...

181
00:23:22.708 --> 00:23:24.291
the bridge looks nicer.

182
00:23:26.125 --> 00:23:29.416
That means photography...

183
00:23:29.833 --> 00:23:33.041
does not reproduce reality.

184
00:23:34.833 --> 00:23:36.500
It depends on how...

185
00:23:37.125 --> 00:23:40.083
the image is framed.

186
00:23:40.458 --> 00:23:42.125
What is revealed.

187
00:23:42.416 --> 00:23:44.291
What is concealed.

188
00:23:45.416 --> 00:23:48.250
Your perspective is critical.

189
00:24:01.333 --> 00:24:04.458
<i>Special Scoop: Spirit Pictures</i>

190
00:24:16.375 --> 00:24:17.875
Jane. you're early.

191
00:24:19.958 --> 00:24:21.708
I'll get it.

192
00:24:27.291 --> 00:24:29.083
Hello? / Hello. Tun.

193
00:24:29.416 --> 00:24:31.625
It's Jane. I'll come by later.

194
00:24:32.625 --> 00:24:33.541
Hello?

195
00:24:33.833 --> 00:24:36.083
Tun. can you hear me?

196
00:24:36.666 --> 00:24:37.750
Hello?

197
00:24:37.791 --> 00:24:38.750
Tun!

198
00:24:39.291 --> 00:24:40.250
Tun!

199
00:24:40.541 --> 00:24:41.583
Hello?

200
00:24:42.750 --> 00:24:43.708
Hello?

201
00:25:12.458 --> 00:25:13.625
What's wrong?

202
00:25:14.500 --> 00:25:15.750
I don't know.

203
00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:18.375
My neck's hurt since the accident.

204
00:25:19.208 --> 00:25:21.250
You should go see a doctor.

205
00:25:22.833 --> 00:25:24.583
I'm sure it's not serious.

206
00:25:27.750 --> 00:25:29.875
What's the use of talking to these spoofs?

207
00:25:31.083 --> 00:25:34.375
<i>Real Ghosts</i>

208
00:25:36.458 --> 00:25:37.833
Are you a reporter?

209
00:25:38.083 --> 00:25:39.125
No.

210
00:25:40.416 --> 00:25:43.208
The funeral foundation sent us.

211
00:25:45.333 --> 00:25:47.833
We run a legal operation.

212
00:25:48.125 --> 00:25:50.416
We have all the right permits.

213
00:26:39.083 --> 00:26:40.375
Excuse me.

214
00:26:40.750 --> 00:26:43.250
Are all these pictures fakes?

215
00:26:44.708 --> 00:26:47.541
Piak! Tell the boss he has guests.

216
00:26:50.250 --> 00:26:51.958
Everyone fakes them.

217
00:26:53.166 --> 00:26:54.333
You know...

218
00:26:54.375 --> 00:26:56.666
these photos are always a hit.

219
00:26:57.750 --> 00:27:00.166
Any issue with them sells out.

220
00:27:00.916 --> 00:27:01.750
But you think...

221
00:27:02.333 --> 00:27:04.541
we can always find real ones?

222
00:27:06.500 --> 00:27:09.000
Isn't that deceiving the public?

223
00:27:10.250 --> 00:27:12.333
Our readers...

224
00:27:12.708 --> 00:27:15.083
want to see scary photos.

225
00:27:16.041 --> 00:27:18.041
They don't want love stories.

226
00:27:19.625 --> 00:27:23.208
Does that mean every photo is fake?

227
00:27:26.333 --> 00:27:28.750
I didn't say that.

228
00:27:42.291 --> 00:27:43.250
Take a look.

229
00:27:44.416 --> 00:27:45.541
See anything?

230
00:27:46.666 --> 00:27:49.583
This is the first photo I had.

231
00:27:50.250 --> 00:27:51.875
I took it at home.

232
00:27:53.541 --> 00:27:55.041
The shadow...

233
00:27:55.083 --> 00:27:57.708
bears a likeness to my mom.

234
00:28:01.166 --> 00:28:03.500
Believe what you will.

235
00:28:05.208 --> 00:28:06.583
But this picture...

236
00:28:07.333 --> 00:28:10.000
was taken after she passed away.

237
00:28:12.333 --> 00:28:13.416
You know...

238
00:28:13.875 --> 00:28:14.916
sometimes...

239
00:28:15.208 --> 00:28:18.041
spirits long for their loved ones.

240
00:28:24.333 --> 00:28:25.958
In my opinion...

241
00:28:26.583 --> 00:28:28.333
these pictures...

242
00:28:29.125 --> 00:28:31.208
represent more than...

243
00:28:31.250 --> 00:28:33.875
macabre urban legends.

244
00:28:35.666 --> 00:28:38.250
They are signs.

245
00:28:42.750 --> 00:28:44.250
Think about it.

246
00:28:45.500 --> 00:28:47.291
Why would the dead...

247
00:28:47.958 --> 00:28:50.166
return to the living...

248
00:28:53.083 --> 00:28:56.375
without a message to convey?

249
00:29:00.416 --> 00:29:02.083
Most importantly...

250
00:29:02.833 --> 00:29:04.708
I believe...

251
00:29:05.375 --> 00:29:06.666
these shadows...

252
00:29:07.708 --> 00:29:10.958
are related to someone in the picture.

253
00:29:14.541 --> 00:29:16.000
A father...

254
00:29:16.375 --> 00:29:17.333
mother...

255
00:29:17.791 --> 00:29:19.333
or lover.

256
00:29:21.333 --> 00:29:22.833
Or someone...

257
00:29:23.333 --> 00:29:25.166
you maligned in life.

258
00:29:49.000 --> 00:29:51.791
How can we tell if they're real...

259
00:29:52.041 --> 00:29:53.333
and not fakes?

260
00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:57.000
What about polaroids?

261
00:30:00.416 --> 00:30:01.750
Can you fake them?

262
00:30:02.583 --> 00:30:04.875
You load the film and press the shutter.

263
00:30:05.375 --> 00:30:07.000
The photo ejects.

264
00:30:25.375 --> 00:30:27.291
Tell me then...

265
00:30:28.125 --> 00:30:30.125
How can they be faked?

266
00:30:34.083 --> 00:30:37.000
How do we know what they want?

267
00:30:37.458 --> 00:30:38.458
Perhaps...

268
00:30:38.708 --> 00:30:41.458
the answer is in the photo.

269
00:30:51.416 --> 00:30:53.708
Two more poses.

270
00:30:54.333 --> 00:30:56.000
Big smiles.

271
00:30:59.416 --> 00:31:02.333
Let's have a different pose.

272
00:31:03.250 --> 00:31:06.166
Embrace her. hold the bouquet...

273
00:31:06.208 --> 00:31:08.583
and kiss her cheek.

274
00:31:10.916 --> 00:31:12.250
Beautiful.

275
00:31:13.750 --> 00:31:15.666
We're done.

276
00:31:16.041 --> 00:31:18.750
Thank you both.

277
00:31:19.125 --> 00:31:21.666
Take them to the dressing room.

278
00:31:47.708 --> 00:31:49.333
What the...

279
00:31:50.958 --> 00:31:52.416
Who's doing that?

280
00:31:52.875 --> 00:31:54.625
Aum. check the fuse!

281
00:31:56.375 --> 00:31:57.666
Hey! Aum!

282
00:32:03.166 --> 00:32:04.666
Who's doing that?

283
00:32:05.791 --> 00:32:07.875
Is it you. Aum?

284
00:32:14.333 --> 00:32:15.291
Who is it?

285
00:32:18.333 --> 00:32:19.833
Who's there!

286
00:32:21.958 --> 00:32:23.416
I asked who it is!

287
00:32:34.125 --> 00:32:36.583
Where are you. Aum?

288
00:32:40.958 --> 00:32:41.958
Who's there!

289
00:33:34.083 --> 00:33:35.458
Please step off the scale.

290
00:33:39.458 --> 00:33:41.541
Step on it again.

291
00:33:49.583 --> 00:33:51.000
Been working hard lately?

292
00:33:51.583 --> 00:33:52.875
Not really.

293
00:33:53.666 --> 00:33:55.250
How long has it hurt?

294
00:33:55.833 --> 00:33:57.666
For quite awhile.

295
00:33:57.708 --> 00:34:00.291
But it's gotten worse lately.

296
00:34:01.208 --> 00:34:03.000
I had a car accident.

297
00:34:03.291 --> 00:34:04.708
