310
00:34:41.541 --> 00:34:42.458
Yes?

311
00:34:43.875 --> 00:34:45.541
Nothing.

312
00:34:50.291 --> 00:34:52.041
Lying bastard.

313
00:34:53.791 --> 00:34:55.791
Lying bastard.

314
00:34:56.333 --> 00:34:57.958
