321
00:35:19.500 --> 00:35:23.125
The male carefully approaches the female.

322
00:35:24.166 --> 00:35:27.750
It hooks itself onto her belly.

323
00:35:28.166 --> 00:35:30.250
And they begin to mate.

324
00:35:31.500 --> 00:35:35.541
The female's response is surprising.

325
00:35:36.666 --> 00:35:40.458
The male becomes her prey.

326
00:35:40.791 --> 00:35:44.791
She slowly eats off his head...

327
00:35:45.541 --> 00:35:48.083
while they are mating.

328
00:35:49.583 --> 00:35:50.916
Eventually...

329
00:35:50.958 --> 00:35:53.500
the male succumbs to death.

330
00:36:02.458 --> 00:36:05.791
Excuse me. where is Room 301?

331
00:36:17.666 --> 00:36:18.625
Jane.

332
00:36:28.916 --> 00:36:29.875
Jane.

333
