342
00:38:32.375 --> 00:38:33.666
Are you drunk?

343
00:38:35.458 --> 00:38:36.666
Those photos...

344
00:38:37.416 --> 00:38:38.666
Where did you hide them?

345
00:38:38.916 --> 00:38:40.208
Give them to me.

346
00:38:42.375 --> 00:38:43.916
Remember that bitch.

347
00:38:43.958 --> 00:38:45.333
Calm down.

348
00:38:46.333 --> 00:38:47.166
What photos?

349
00:38:47.416 --> 00:38:49.208
Just give them to me!

350
00:38:49.458 --> 00:38:51.458
Please calm down.

351
00:38:52.375 --> 00:38:54.208
Tonn. calm down.

352
00:38:54.500 --> 00:38:56.500
What photos?

353
00:39:01.416 --> 00:39:02.458
Tonn.

354
00:39:02.750 --> 00:39:04.833
I'll call your wife.

355
00:39:49.000 --> 00:39:50.333
What are you doing?

356
00:39:52.166 --> 00:39:53.750
Cleaning up.

357
00:39:59.875 --> 00:40:01.583
Your neck still sore?

358
00:40:03.750 --> 00:40:04.958
Yeah.

359
00:40:05.000 --> 00:40:07.583
Take it easy. Don't work so much.

360
00:44:48.375 --> 00:44:50.875
Natrenapa Chan-ngam. Honor Society 1995

361
00:45:03.125 --> 00:45:04.166
Tonn.

362
00:45:05.458 --> 00:45:06.708
It's Tun.

363
00:45:08.666 --> 00:45:10.041
