364
00:45:24.875 --> 00:45:25.916
Tonn.

365
00:45:28.500 --> 00:45:29.958
Are you home?

366
00:45:39.208 --> 00:45:40.250
Tonn.

367
00:46:06.458 --> 00:46:08.041
Natrenapa Chan-ngam

368
00:46:56.416 --> 00:46:57.375
Tonn!

369
00:46:58.791 --> 00:46:59.750
Tonn!

370
00:47:01.750 --> 00:47:02.708
Tonn!

371
00:47:10.458 --> 00:47:12.166
Tonn!

372
00:47:50.041 --> 00:47:51.750
I'm really sorry.

373
00:47:52.833 --> 00:47:54.125
Do you know...

374
00:47:54.458 --> 00:47:56.208
what was bothering him?

375
00:48:00.166 --> 00:48:01.791
No. Suddenly he...

376
00:48:01.833 --> 00:48:04.625
It's your gang's fault.

377
00:48:06.708 --> 00:48:08.375
Have you all gone insane?

378
00:48:09.875 --> 00:48:11.750
