395
00:50:18.750 --> 00:50:21.166
We all thought she was weird.

396
00:50:26.125 --> 00:50:27.958
I felt sorry for her.

397
00:50:35.375 --> 00:50:38.208
We dated but I kept it secret.

398
00:50:41.333 --> 00:50:43.166
She loved me a lot.

399
00:53:41.083 --> 00:53:43.583
She threatened to slit her wrists.

400
00:53:44.750 --> 00:53:46.833
I didn't know what to do.

401
00:53:46.875 --> 00:53:49.083
My friends thought it was funny.

402
00:53:49.125 --> 00:53:51.375
How were they involved?

403
00:53:51.416 --> 00:53:53.083
Why are they dead?

404
00:53:53.416 --> 00:53:54.166
They...

405
00:53:54.666 --> 00:53:56.333
What did they do?

406
00:53:58.541 --> 00:54:00.000
I don't know.

407
00:54:01.625 --> 00:54:04.208
Tonn said he'd take care of it.

408
00:54:07.666 --> 00:54:10.166
After that. Natre disappeared.

409
00:54:11.375 --> 00:54:13.625
I never saw her again.

410
00:54:14.666 --> 00:54:17.333
Didn't you try to stop them?

411
00:54:19.000 --> 00:54:21.375
How could you let it happen?

412
00:54:28.625 --> 00:54:30.625
What could I do?

413
00:54:32.791 --> 00:54:34.916
Now everyone is dead.

414
00:54:38.458 --> 00:54:39.500
I'm...

415
00:54:40.333 --> 00:54:42.250
I'm going to die next.

416
00:55:22.208 --> 00:55:23.708
It's funny how...

417
00:55:25.958 --> 00:55:28.458
we always say...

418
00:55:28.875 --> 00:55:31.541
if we could turn back time...

419
00:55:32.583 --> 00:55:33.750
we...

420
00:55:33.791 --> 00:55:36.416
we would reverse all our wrongs.

421
00:55:39.500 --> 00:55:41.583
Do you think she's okay?

422
00:55:42.666 --> 00:55:44.625
Will she be there?

423
00:55:44.666 --> 00:55:45.916
Go to sleep.

424
00:55:48.416 --> 00:55:50.416
I'll keep you company tonight.

425
00:57:59.916 --> 00:58:01.458
Excuse me.

426
00:58:02.583 --> 00:58:04.416
Do you have any toilet paper?

427
00:58:40.583 --> 00:58:42.166
Can I poo first?

428
00:58:42.208 --> 00:58:43.250
I'm sorry.

429
00:59:55.583 --> 00:59:57.000
What's bothering you?

430
01:00:12.041 --> 01:00:13.291
What's wrong?

431
01:00:25.458 --> 01:00:26.250
What is it?

432
01:01:20.625 --> 01:01:22.708
Is it around here?

433
01:01:33.750 --> 01:01:34.916
Excuse me.

434
01:01:35.291 --> 01:01:36.708
Do you know where this is?

435
01:01:41.250 --> 01:01:43.458
Mom. where is this house?

436
01:02:18.541 --> 01:02:19.666
Ma'am.

437
01:02:33.083 --> 01:02:34.333
Excuse me...

438
01:02:34.375 --> 01:02:36.333
Is this Natre's house?

439
01:02:37.916 --> 01:02:39.333
What do you want?

440
01:02:40.458 --> 01:02:41.458
Well...

441
01:02:41.916 --> 01:02:44.291
We're her friends.

442
01:02:45.416 --> 01:02:47.916
Natre's friends? Come inside.

443
01:02:58.833 --> 01:03:01.541
Have some water. You must be tired.

444
01:03:01.791 --> 01:03:03.791
Did you drive from Bangkok?

445
01:03:04.833 --> 01:03:06.000
Yes.

446
01:03:10.625 --> 01:03:13.041
We'd like to ask about Natre.

447
01:03:14.500 --> 01:03:16.000
She's not feeling well.

448
01:03:16.375 --> 01:03:18.291
She's taking a nap.

449
01:03:19.416 --> 01:03:21.125
Should I wake her?

450
01:03:25.416 --> 01:03:27.250
Stay for dinner.

451
01:03:27.958 --> 01:03:29.333
I was about to cook.

452
01:03:29.583 --> 01:03:32.166
I'm making her favorite dish.

453
01:03:33.750 --> 01:03:35.708
Natre will be so happy.

454
01:03:35.750 --> 01:03:38.000
Her friends don't visit often.

455
01:03:38.333 --> 01:03:40.000
Wait right here.

456
01:03:59.666 --> 01:04:01.041
Where are you going?

457
01:05:19.000 --> 01:05:20.458
How dare you?

458
01:05:26.375 --> 01:05:28.541
Did she commit suicide?

459
01:05:33.458 --> 01:05:35.791
We should cremate her.

460
01:05:37.958 --> 01:05:39.041
No.

461
01:05:39.083 --> 01:05:40.875
I won't cremate her.

462
01:05:42.916 --> 01:05:44.125
Ma'am...

463
01:05:45.500 --> 01:05:48.750
I don't know if you believe such things...

464
01:05:49.041 --> 01:05:52.541
but I'd like you to look at these photos.

465
01:05:53.458 --> 01:05:57.208
They were taken around campus.

466
01:05:59.291 --> 01:06:02.166
Some of the places...

467
01:06:02.666 --> 01:06:05.583
were rooms Natre had been in.

468
01:06:08.000 --> 01:06:11.125
And these shadows appeared.

469
01:06:14.083 --> 01:06:15.500
I think that...

470
01:06:16.708 --> 01:06:20.208
Natre's spirit is restless.

471
01:06:21.666 --> 01:06:22.833
Natre...

472
01:06:26.625 --> 01:06:28.250
My dear Natre.

473
01:06:30.625 --> 01:06:32.666
Why don't you visit me?

474
01:06:41.458 --> 01:06:44.166
Can you tell me what happened?

475
01:06:44.708 --> 01:06:46.625
Why she left Bangkok?

476
01:06:55.375 --> 01:06:56.541
Ma'am...

477
01:06:58.958 --> 01:07:00.000
Ma'am.

478
01:07:01.666 --> 01:07:03.541
These shadows...

479
01:07:03.875 --> 01:07:07.666
might mean her spirit is not at peace.

480
01:07:12.000 --> 01:07:14.666
We should hold her funeral.

481
01:07:15.958 --> 01:07:17.000
Please.

482
01:07:31.958 --> 01:07:33.625
When she came home...

483
01:07:33.666 --> 01:07:35.125
she seemed different.

484
01:07:35.458 --> 01:07:37.458
She wouldn't talk to anyone.

485
01:07:37.791 --> 01:07:40.333
No one knows what happened in Bangkok.

486
01:07:41.833 --> 01:07:44.416
Then she overdosed on pills.

487
01:07:45.000 --> 01:07:47.750
Luckily. her mother found her...

488
01:07:47.791 --> 01:07:50.041
and got her to the hospital on time.

489
01:07:50.333 --> 01:07:52.875
When she recovered...

490
01:07:54.041 --> 01:07:57.250
she climbed on the hospital roof...

491
01:07:57.750 --> 01:07:59.625
and jumped off the edge.

492
01:08:01.416 --> 01:08:04.666
Why wouldn't her mom cremate her?

493
01:08:06.625 --> 01:08:10.291
She's been distraught ever since Natre's death.

494
01:08:10.875 --> 01:08:14.416
No matter what she refused to cremate her.

495
01:08:15.958 --> 01:08:18.333
All the villagers were scared.

496
01:08:18.666 --> 01:08:21.791
No one wanted to socialize with her.

497
01:10:29.291 --> 01:10:30.708
Can't sleep?

498
01:10:36.625 --> 01:10:38.958
Tell me the truth...

499
01:10:39.750 --> 01:10:41.583
Did you love Natre?

500
01:10:45.666 --> 01:10:47.541
I tried to...

501
01:10:53.875 --> 01:10:56.791
I believed that one day I would.

502
01:11:02.375 --> 01:11:04.708
But I was fooling myself.

503
01:11:12.666 --> 01:11:14.541
When I broke it off...

504
01:11:15.500 --> 01:11:18.333
I was a total asshole.

505
01:11:24.416 --> 01:11:26.750
But she still loved me the same.

506
01:11:33.291 --> 01:11:35.250
I want this to be over.

507
01:11:37.333 --> 01:11:39.583
If she wants me to die I will.

508
01:11:40.958 --> 01:11:42.666
Don't say that.

509
01:11:43.666 --> 01:11:45.583
It's almost over.

510
01:11:46.791 --> 01:11:48.208
No it's not.

511
01:11:53.458 --> 01:11:55.833
I know she'll come for me.

512
01:11:56.666 --> 01:11:57.875
Tun.

513
01:11:58.625 --> 01:12:00.791
We've come this far.

514
01:12:03.208 --> 01:12:05.208
And you're sorry for what you did.

515
01:12:05.916 --> 01:12:07.666
I'm sure she knows.

516
01:12:09.958 --> 01:12:12.291
Don't talk about death anymore.

517
01:12:19.250 --> 01:12:20.416
I'm sorry.

518
01:12:26.416 --> 01:12:28.541
Do you still love me?

519
01:12:34.416 --> 01:12:37.000
No matter what you won't leave me. right?

520
01:14:20.833 --> 01:14:21.750
Jane.

521
01:14:22.083 --> 01:14:23.083
Jane.

522
01:16:00.000 --> 01:16:01.125
Tun...

523
01:16:01.666 --> 01:16:02.666
Jane...

524
01:16:03.125 --> 01:16:04.916
Where did you go?

525
01:16:06.166 --> 01:16:07.458
Why did you leave me alone?

526
01:16:08.541 --> 01:16:10.291
We've got to leave.

527
01:16:13.541 --> 01:16:15.000
Asshole!

528
01:16:16.291 --> 01:16:17.958
Why did you leave me?

529
01:16:18.208 --> 01:16:19.916
Didn't you love me?

530
01:16:20.375 --> 01:16:21.833
How could you leave me?

531
01:16:24.916 --> 01:16:27.500
How could you leave me?

532
01:18:10.375 --> 01:18:11.375
Tun...

533
01:18:12.041 --> 01:18:13.750
Are you feeling better?

534
01:18:16.208 --> 01:18:18.166
What happened last night?

535
01:18:19.625 --> 01:18:20.708
Tun...

536
01:18:22.458 --> 01:18:23.500
Jane...

537
01:18:23.833 --> 01:18:25.041
Jane...

538
01:18:32.333 --> 01:18:33.708
The abbot said...

539
01:18:33.750 --> 01:18:36.041
Natre will be cremated today.

540
01:18:39.500 --> 01:18:41.083
It's over.

541
01:20:41.708 --> 01:20:43.750
Hello. / Hello. Jane.

542
01:20:44.000 --> 01:20:45.583
Picking up photos?

543
01:20:45.875 --> 01:20:47.083
Where's Tun?

544
01:20:47.125 --> 01:20:48.333
He's busy.

545
01:20:48.791 --> 01:20:49.833
Good.

546
01:20:50.166 --> 01:20:51.500
When he's busy...

547
01:20:51.541 --> 01:20:52.958
I get to see you.

548
01:21:00.625 --> 01:21:02.958
You went on vacation?

549
01:21:03.541 --> 01:21:05.166
To the beach.

550
01:21:05.208 --> 01:21:06.708
When did you go?

551
01:21:07.250 --> 01:21:09.000
Last week.

552
01:21:12.208 --> 01:21:13.916
This photo is...

553
01:21:16.916 --> 01:21:18.291
What's wrong?

554
01:21:24.458 --> 01:21:25.583
You look fatter.

555
01:21:28.125 --> 01:21:30.250
I didn't recognize you.

556
01:21:32.375 --> 01:21:33.500
Hi.

557
01:21:34.541 --> 01:21:35.625
Jumbo prints.

558
01:21:37.375 --> 01:21:38.625
Write your name. please.

559
01:24:24.791 --> 01:24:26.166
Get her guys!

560
01:25:03.375 --> 01:25:04.375
Jane...

561
01:25:05.375 --> 01:25:06.958
Why are you crying?

562
01:25:09.750 --> 01:25:10.750
Asshole...

563
01:25:13.625 --> 01:25:15.250
How could you be so cruel?

564
01:25:21.583 --> 01:25:22.875
Where did you find these?

565
01:25:25.541 --> 01:25:27.375
If I didn't find them...

566
01:25:27.625 --> 01:25:30.208
I'd be a fool forever. right?

567
01:25:35.750 --> 01:25:37.583
Let me explain.

568
01:25:40.833 --> 01:25:42.833
What's there to say?

569
01:25:47.000 --> 01:25:49.083
I always believed you.

570
01:25:56.000 --> 01:25:58.166
I thought I knew you.

571
01:26:12.666 --> 01:26:13.875
Tun.

572
01:26:15.041 --> 01:26:16.333
Take her picture...

573
01:26:16.375 --> 01:26:17.666
so she doesn't blab.

574
01:26:18.125 --> 01:26:20.083
Tun. help me.

575
01:26:21.708 --> 01:26:23.250
I know it was wrong.

576
01:26:24.750 --> 01:26:26.666
Take her picture now!

577
01:26:27.750 --> 01:26:29.000
What's wrong!

578
01:26:30.666 --> 01:26:32.208
I'm your buddy!

579
01:26:32.666 --> 01:26:33.916
Hurry!

580
01:26:42.666 --> 01:26:44.875
Tun. help me.

581
01:26:58.708 --> 01:27:00.500
I never forgave myself.

582
01:27:00.750 --> 01:27:02.500
But I was young and stupid.

583
01:27:04.041 --> 01:27:05.583
I've heard enough.

584
01:27:07.500 --> 01:27:09.458
I'm going home.

585
01:28:06.250 --> 01:28:07.666
Come on out!

586
01:28:12.541 --> 01:28:13.833
Where are you?

587
01:28:20.916 --> 01:28:22.750
I thought you loved me!

588
01:28:25.083 --> 01:28:27.041
Loved me so much!

589
01:28:34.583 --> 01:28:36.833
Till death do us part!

590
01:28:42.291 --> 01:28:43.958
She's gone now.

591
01:30:27.666 --> 01:30:28.750
Sometimes...

592
01:30:28.791 --> 01:30:30.873
